<item>
            <title>[LU-18249] RPM: Migrate ofed (ofa_kernel modules) requires to MOFED o2iblnd module package</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18249</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current RPM packaging build for MOFED places an external dependency requirement on kmod-mlnx-ofa_kernel / mlnx-ofa_kernel-kmp for all the lustre packages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the case of user-space packages there should be no direct dependency on the 3rd party OFED, it should only apply to the actual kernel module package that requires MOFED.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This enables the use case where build servers build with an external MOFED and in-kernel users can install the distributed rpms and choose the in-kernel package with out hitting a MOFED requires.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="84697">LU-18249</key>
            <summary>RPM: Migrate ofed (ofa_kernel modules) requires to MOFED o2iblnd module package</summary>
